# vi/vim cheatsheet
https://vim.rtorr.com/


i : enter insert mode
v : visual mode 
esc : global mode 

## global mode 
dd : delete line 
u : undo 
H : move cursor to top
G : move cursor to bottom
/<string> : find string
    n : next matched string
    N : previous matched string

:set number : show line number 
:<number>  : go to line number

## visual mode 

to comment multiple lines
v : visual mode -> up/down to select multiple lines -> :s/^ /# / + enter

